data.description: Welcome home to country living in this lovely ranch-style home w/a full walkout basement. High speed Xfinity Comcast internet & NO HOA! Tucked away on almost 7 acres, this home has over 3,800 Sqft, 4 BDRMS, 3.5 BTHS, LVP flooring, tilt-in Low E grade windows & that sought after open layout. Family room w/vaulted ceilings is open to the gourmet eat-in kitchen that showcases granite counters, center island, white cabinets & SS appliances (air fryer oven). Primary en suite features a walk-in closet w/shelving, double vanity, soaking tub & separate tile shower w/a bench. Walkout basement has a family room, full BTH, workshop, craft & storage room! This home would make the perfect farmette w/the run-in shed that is already in place (fencing would need to be added), but horses are permitted. Covered front porch, back deck & patio, salt water swimming pool, gazebo & fire pit! Paved driveway & the large concrete parking pad also has a space for an RV or boat. There is a 30 AMP outlet hookup for your RV, carport for storing your boat or tractor, shed & chicken coop! Great location minutes to Lake Anna state park, marinas to launch your boat & spend the day on the lake, dining & much more!
